## UI Systems Already Built — Do Not Rebuild

These systems are complete. Reuse them; don't rework unless you have a specific assignment to do so.

### HUD layout (`game/ui/hud.py`)

- **`_compute_layout(surface)`** — derives all rects from `surface.get_size()`. Never hardcode `1920×1080`.
- **Top bar** (48px): Gold, Heroes, Enemies, Wave, help hint, mode banner
- **Bottom bar** (80px): Minimap frame, command bar (Build/Hire/Bounty icons + hotkeys)
- **Right panel** (300–380px, hidden by default): selected hero/building info. Toggle with Tab. `self.right_panel_visible` flag.
- **Messages** (top-left transient): `hud.messages` list, auto-expire after `message_duration` ms.
- **Help overlay**: `self.show_help`, toggled by F3, default OFF. Cached surface (`_help_panel_cache`).

### Pause/settings menu (`game/ui/pause_menu.py`)

- `PauseMenu(screen_width, screen_height, engine=None, audio_system=None)`
- Pages: `"main"` → `"graphics"` / `"audio"` / `"controls"` (and back)
- `menu.open()`, `menu.close()`, `menu.toggle()`
- `menu.handle_click(pos)` → returns action string or None
- `menu.handle_mousemove(pos)` and `menu.handle_mouseup(pos)` — for volume slider drag
- `menu.on_resize(w, h)` — call when window size changes
- Requires `engine.request_display_settings()` or `engine.apply_display_settings()` for Graphics page
- Requires `audio_system.get/set_master_volume()` for Audio page

### Build catalog (`game/ui/build_catalog_panel.py`)

- Opened when castle is selected → "Build Buildings" button in castle panel
- Centered grid of all building types with name, cost, hotkey, thumbnail/swatch
- Click on available building → calls `engine.select_building_for_placement(type)`
- `catalog.on_resize(w, h)` — call when window size changes

