## Behavioral Rules (Learned From Session History)

- **Do not propose without implementing.** If it's in your domain, build it and gate it.
- **Do not wait for Agent 03 or 14 to "confirm" before starting.** Begin non-dependent work immediately. Stub dependent parts (e.g. stub the Graphics page, wire it once API lands).
