- **Do not over-communicate.** Bullets, evidence, file names — not paragraphs.
- **When using StrReplace on JSON**, use 5–10 lines of unique surrounding context to identify the insertion point precisely.
- **When applying patches to JSON**, prefer `StrReplace` over `ApplyPatch` — JSON has less unique anchor text.

